data.description: Indulge in this beautiful exquisite home nestled in the charming Alum Rock neighborhood of San Jose within walking distance to Alum Rock park and Country Club. With its open floor plan and tasteful designer final finishes, this residence offers a truly captivating and contemporary living space. The original floors, along with the A/C and heating system, ensure optimal comfort year-round, while the double-pane windows invite an abundance of natural light to illuminate every corner. The expansive lot provides ample room for an ADU unit or a delightful outdoor area, perfect for hosting unforgettable gatherings. Situated in the highly sought-after East Foothills neighborhood, this single-story haven offers a serene escape from the fast-paced city life, without compromising on urban convenience. The elegant wood floors, coupled with the generous natural light, create an ambiance of warmth and tranquility. And with the addition of a charming gazebo area, this home truly has it all. Don't let this opportunity pass you by - seize the chance to make this your next cherished "Home".
